# EcoAscent is a client-only app — no environment variables are required to run it.
# This file is intentionally kept as a placeholder to document env-var discipline
# for future backend integrations (Lovable Cloud / Supabase, analytics, etc.).
#
# Example for a future backend:
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
# VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=